videos.description: With less than seven seconds left and tied at 94-94, Stephen Thompson Jr. drains the game-winning 3-pointer to lead the Beavers to victory in double-overtime against the Huskies.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Thompson sinks dagger on Washington at buzzer
